(10581, 914, 'team_1_role', 'Partner'),
(10582, 914, '_team_1_role', 'field_58be26f8d5a69'),
(10583, 914, 'team_1_bio', 'You tell your story, and I see it unfold in living color--including its potential to make the world a better place. Does that sound cheesy? My mom will tell you it’s in my DNA to look for what matters, poking and prodding for the right place to build a bridge between where you are and where you want to be. All the while, I’m mentally skimming my Rolodex for new friends you need to know who complement your cause with theirs.  I’m dogged (some say stubborn) and refuse to accept any result but the best. Because it’s your baby—and we spread the word about goodness for a higher purpose.\r\n \r\nWhen not working, I’m browsing an estate sale for treasures or enjoying my wildflowers in the Texas Hill Country with my chuck-wagon cooking husband, Rick, our four-grown children, and our ever-expanding family and friends, who keep me laughing.'),
