(15476, 1003, 'testimonial_slides_0_slide', '"We all know that people must ‘hear’ about books before they will ‘buy’ books. When I wrote my book: Things I Wish I’d Known Before We Got Married, it was Lovell-Fairchild Communications who ‘got the word out’ for me. Hundreds of thousands of young couples have now been ‘helped’ because they ‘heard’; they ‘bought’; they read. I highly recommend Lovell-Fairchild Communications.'),
(15477, 1003, '_testimonial_slides_0_slide', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(15478, 1003, 'testimonial_slides_0_author', 'Gary Chapman, <br>Ph.D. author of The Five Love Languages.'),
