(15482, 1003, 'testimonial_slides_1_slide', '"Lovell-Fairchild has amassed the best reputation across the Christian media that I have ever seen, and they command a professional respect from the media, churches, and parachurch ministries across this nation. They have deep networks, they are creative, trustworthy, and know how to tell your story while keeping it your story."'),
(15483, 1003, '_testimonial_slides_1_slide', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
