(15708, 1004, 'testimonial_slides_1_content', 'Lovell-Fairchild has amassed the best reputation across the Christian media that I have ever seen, and they command a professional respect from the media, churches, and parachurch ministries across this nation. They have deep networks, they are creative, trustworthy, and know how to tell your story while keeping it your story.'),
(15709, 1004, '_testimonial_slides_1_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(15710, 1004, 'testimonial_slides_2_content', 'I have found Lovell-Fairchild to be insightful and strategic counselors who bring a high level of professional integrity and creativity to their work. As one of the few agencies in the faith-based niche, I have known Lovell-Fairchild to be world class media planners with extensive press contacts that have proven invaluable to the Potter\'s House over the years. They are excellent partners who bring a great deal of thoughtfulness, big picture thinking, and tireless execution to every assignment.'),
