(16915, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_6_slide', '"Their network and know-how were great assets to our efforts. Their staff diligently executed and moved fast to capitalize on emerging opportunities."'),
(16916, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_6_slide', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16917, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_6_author', 'Andrea Lee, <br>Winshape Foundation'),
(16918, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_6_author', 'field_595d634685188'),
(16919, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_0_content', 'We all know that people must ‘hear’ about books before they will ‘buy’ books. When I wrote my book: Things I Wish I’d Known Before We Got Married, it was Lovell-Fairchild Communications who ‘got the word out’ for me. Hundreds of thousands of young couples have now been ‘helped’ because they ‘heard’; they ‘bought’; they read. I highly recommend Lovell-Fairchild Communications.'),
(16920, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_0_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16921, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_1_content', 'Lovell-Fairchild has amassed the best reputation across the Christian media that I have ever seen, and they command a professional respect from the media, churches, and parachurch ministries across this nation. They have deep networks, they are creative, trustworthy, and know how to tell your story while keeping it your story.'),
(16922, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_1_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16923, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_2_content', 'I have found Lovell-Fairchild to be insightful and strategic counselors who bring a high level of professional integrity and creativity to their work. As one of the few agencies in the faith-based niche, I have known Lovell-Fairchild to be world class media planners with extensive press contacts that have proven invaluable to the Potter\'s House over the years. They are excellent partners who bring a great deal of thoughtfulness, big picture thinking, and tireless execution to every assignment.'),
(16924, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_2_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16925, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_3_content', 'I have worked with Lovell-Fairchild Communications for over 10 years to promote and market a variety of books, films and other projects. I have found them to be people of integrity who came along side us and helped us deliver our projects to the market with excellence. They are a one stop shop for promotion and marketing; with a variety of skilled professionals and I would wholeheartedly endorse them to anyone who needs public relations or marketing support. Nancy Lovell and Julie Fairchild and their team of professionals are some of the best people I have ever worked with.'),
(16926, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_3_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16927, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_4_content', 'Their network and know-how were great assets to our efforts. Their staff diligently executed and moved fast to capitalize on emerging opportunities.\r\n'),
(16928, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_4_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16929, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_5_content', 'I am impressed by the quality of their work, but even moreso by their personal commitment to us as clients.'),
(16930, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_5_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16931, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_6_content', 'Their network and know-how were great assets to our efforts. Their staff diligently executed and moved fast to capitalize on emerging opportunities.'),
(16932, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_6_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16933, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_7_content', 'Lovell-Fairchild, here in Dallas, does such an awesome job of connecting media with key leaders.'),
(16934, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_7_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16935, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_7_author', 'Tom Tradup,<br> V.P./News & Talk Programming. SALEM Radio Network™'),
(16936, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_7_author', 'field_595d634685188'),
(16937, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_8_content', 'Lovell-Fairchild Communications is ALL IN for their clients. They are not only responsive, but are pro-active. They come to you with the idea first, where other firms typically ride the wave you have already generated for yourself and just manage what the client already does. <br><br>\r\n\r\nLovell-Fairchild takes the time to learn the client\'s voice. So many times we have encountered square pegs and round holes. They realize there is not one size fits all, and while they will educate you and try to take you places you haven’t gone before, they will not set you up for failure. In my experience, and we have had many, there hasn’t been an equal that we have worked with.'),
(16938, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_8_content', 'field_595d61a30fa56'),
(16939, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_8_author', 'Sandy Parker,<br> Executive Producer Four Blood Moons'),
(16940, 1029, '_testimonial_slides_8_author', 'field_595d634685188'),
(16941, 1029, 'testimonial_slides_9_content', 'From the start of our work together, Lovell-Fairchild thought with us, and often ahead of us. We valued their connections, ideas, organization, teamwork . . . and, of course, the media coverage.'),
