(400, 1, '2017-04-14 21:51:07', '2017-04-14 21:51:07', 'Walking Together in the Right Direction\r\n\r\nA guiding compass through real parenting issues as moms and dads share life\r\nstories of how God and His Word give direction.\r\nThis Telly Award-winning Christian parenting series launches online March 4,\r\n2016. Across 12 inaugural episodes, from multiple races and socioeconomic\r\nstrata, in Parent Compass, mothers and fathers open up with often surprising\r\nstories of how their own upbringings and pasts, their marriage and life\r\nmanagement, their child rearing and the faith factor . . . all reveal God’s direction\r\nin daily parenting.', 'Parent Compass', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'parent-compass', '', '', '2017-07-12 16:34:30', '2017-07-12 16:34:30', '', 0, 'http://lovell-fairchild.dev//?post_type=clients&#038;p=400', 119, 'clients', '', 0),
