(1091, 1, '2017-07-12 22:34:10', '2017-07-12 22:34:10', 'Samantha Crawford is living a storybook life: she’s happily married, she lives on a ranch where she keeps her beloved horse, and the stories she’s told and illustrated since childhood have become published books.\r\n\r\nWhen her husband Billy is killed in a senseless act of violence, Sam loses her faith and her will to live. But a death-defying encounter with two children leads to a reunion with Joe, her oldest friend. Inspired by true events, UNCONDITIONAL stars Michael Ealy (Think Like A Man) and Lynn Collins (John Carter).\r\n\r\nAs Sam watches “Papa” Joe care for and love the kids in his under-resourced neighborhood, she begins to realize that no matter life’s circumstances, the love of God is always reaching out to us.', 'Unconditional', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'unconditional-the-book', '', '', '2017-07-12 22:34:10', '2017-07-12 22:34:10', '', 0, 'http://lovell-fairchild.dev/?post_type=clients&#038;p=1091', 260, 'clients', '', 0),
